// REV. LOVEJOY

"Rev. Lovejoy: Thanks a lot, Marge. That was our only burlesque house.",
"Rev. Lovejoy: Today's Christian doesn't think he needs God. He's got his Hi-Fi, his boob tube, and his instant pizza pie...",
"Rev. Lovejoy: Get a divorce.<p>Helen Lovejoy: Mmm-hmm.<p>Marge: But isn't that a sin?<p>Rev. Lovejoy: Marge, just about everything is a sin. (Holds up a Bible) You ever sat down and read this thing? Technically, we're not allowed to go to the bathroom.",
