"Mr. Burns: Just sign this form, and the money will be yours. Muhahahahaha... Ahem. Sorry, I was just um, eh, um, thinking of something funny Smithers did today.<p>Smithers: I didn't do anything funny today.<p>Mr. Burns: Shut! up!",
"Mr. Burns: Are you acquainted with our state's stringent usury laws?<p>Homer: Usury?<p>Mr. Burns: Oh, silly me! I must've just made up a word that doesn't exist.",
