"Mr. Burns: Now, what was I laughing about? Oh, yes, that dead Irishman. (Starts laughing again)",
"Mr. Burns: Release the League of Evil. (Wall opens to reveal a table with skeletons at it) What happened to my league?<p>Smithers: Even monsters need air, sir.",
